**EXPRESSIONS OF INTEREST PRE-RELEASE - DATE TO BE CONFIRMED**

CBRE are proud to present this significant development site as a rare opportunity for a developer or speculative land owner to acquire a site in the tightly held main street location of Prospect Road

Located only 5.5km's from the Adelaide CBD, Prospect Road has undergone significant revitalisation in recent years

This substantial land holding of 1,765sqm* is zoned Urban Corridor by the City of Prospect allowing for a broad range of potential uses including retail, office or high density residential

Substantial existing improvements offering short to medium term leasing opportunities

High profile corner location with 30 metre street frontage to Prospect Road and access from Milner Street

The City of Prospect is known to be a very pro-active council when it comes to supporting development, in particular for those properties located along Prospect Road

Please don't hesitate to contact one of the selling agents to discuss this outstanding opportunity in further detail.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE South Australian Metropolitan Investments is pleased to offer to the market, one of the best development sites of 2018. 

Located amongst the established high profile residential suburb of Prospect, 69-73 Prospect Road offers developers a corner site with substantial existing holding income. The property is in close proximity to infrastructure key to establishing the fantastic residential amenity that Prospect presents in the Palace Nova Cinemas directly adjacent, Coles Supermarket & cosmopolitan cafes and restaurants all within 500m walk.

CBRE further highlight the below development characteristics set to appeal to developers of all categories:

- Massive site area of 2,760sqm*
- Urban Corridor Zoning – High Street Policy Area
- Development up to 4 storeys permitted (STCC)
- Corner site with frontage of 53m* to Prospect Road
- Three existing certificates of title
- Fantastic residential amenity near Prospect Cinemas
- Gross holding income of $103,902.62pa* 
- Mixed use development site suited to high density residential, retail, commercial or aged care

For Sale by Expressions of Interest closing Thursday 6th September 2018 @ 4pm

Council’s consolidation and 4 level redevelopment adjacent the Town Hall allows for the creation of this new allotment.  This is the first opportunity to purchase a site that has never before been offered to the market for sale.

This significant site of 1372sqm* offers great exposure within the Multi-Award Winning Prospect Village Heart, a thriving café and retail mainstreet precinct on Prospect Road with low vacancy rates and many other exciting developments (including the new 14 screen cinema) underway and coming soon.  Access to fast broadband services and located in amongst thriving co-working spaces, this is one of the hottest properties of this scale to hit the Adelaide market for years.

Prospect Road frontage of 30m* for high exposure plus rear access via Olive Street.

The adjoining property to the South is set to undergo a significant four level redevelopment, providing a brand new facility with an integrated Civic Centre, Community Hub, Library and Innovation Centre for the growing community and business sector which will further enhance the appeal and amenity of what is already one of Adelaide’s most progressive retail main streets.

This is an opportunity to work alongside City of Prospect to develop something truly special.

Zoned Urban Corridor (High Street Policy Area) promoting development of 4 storeys (plus basement), City of Prospect awaits your EoI outlining various forms of flexible accommodation with a range of commercial, retail and residential uses promoted (STNC).

What an amazing and high profile location in the Village Heart precinct and an opportunity not to be missed!

For sale by Expressions of Interest closing Thursday 24th August at 4.00pm (ACST).
